{"tid":2058734,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[父母離婚入] 點樣供養父母","createTime":"2020-06-10T11:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T12:51:57.000Z","uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"39e710076b672e7eef970ca3e8abdd9644d69663","tid":2058734,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"我19歲，讀緊書<br />\n但諗到第時翻工要俾家用就覺得好煩<br />\n老豆老母細細個已經離婚<br />\n我跟老母住，但咁多年嚟老豆一直有俾贍養費同聯絡<br />\n但老豆一直都單身寡佬咁<br />\n<br />\n老豆老母都55歲上下，我諗我讀完書做一兩年嘢佢地就退休，我老豆冇強積金，好似旨意晒第時我養<br />\n但我真係唔知道a唔afford得到同時分開養兩邊<br />\n<br />\n有冇人老豆老母離婚，你地點面對已經分開咗嗰邊<br />\n家用點俾，多唔多見面"},{"pid":"2a378e723318a2b486ccecf7b024553ec4c32400","tid":2058734,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ade5c55bf9a353bb2ec9842f34ba008f230a83","tid":2058734,"uid":328316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"兩個都唔好養 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fe6fd9c3a056a0be5a4d85f05d0a3fd9cb3433","tid":2058734,"uid":40927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"兩個都唔養，自己都未養得掂，諗掂自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b529757f6fa18b1609cd014fac5144c22f088659","tid":2058734,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:45:51.000Z","msg":"老綜上車未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270826014c36105f7deb4ddcd21f4682f7818ed0","tid":2058734,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a378e723318a2b486ccecf7b024553ec4c32400","tid":2058734,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"問過好多朋友，最大負擔既都係我<br />\n個個一係啊爸啊媽得四十幾歲<br />\n就算單親，同老豆都唔會聯絡<br />\n有啲話煩緊條女要結婚<br />\n我呢啲真係連結婚都唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8d5c6178427e3b5992340e383db418a7f45308","tid":2058734,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"270826014c36105f7deb4ddcd21f4682f7818ed0","tid":2058734,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a378e723318a2b486ccecf7b024553ec4c32400","tid":2058734,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"問過好多朋友，最大負擔既都係我<br />\n個個一係啊爸啊媽得四十幾歲<br />\n就算單親，同老豆都唔會聯絡<br />\n有啲話煩緊條女要結婚<br />\n我呢啲真係連結婚都唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:51:16.000Z","msg":"有能力就養，無料就收皮做自私撚啦。 我都係食屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ad655851dbe28667837791b2e35ef779964801","tid":2058734,"uid":328316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:52:16.000Z","msg":"唔撚好養囉<br />\n佢兩老野都幾十歲唔擺得耐啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢緊係留返自己FING <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bc2a56e7159b6be1101ff59251ae8d0ba5f740","tid":2058734,"uid":26666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9133338bd0f9397b4d19d9ea844780eb18876d","tid":2058734,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"$2000 老豆<br />\n$4000 老媽 因為一齊住<br />\n<br />\n然